管.definition: to take care (of); to control; to manage; to be in charge of; to look after; to run; to care about; tube; pipe; woodwind; classifier for tube-shaped objects; particle similar to 把[ba3] in 管...叫 constructions; writing brush; (coll.) to; towards

管不著.definition: to have no right or ability to interfere in sth; it's none of your business!

管中窺豹.definition: lit. to see a leopard through a narrow tube (idiom); fig. to miss the big picture

管他.definition: no matter if; regardless of; don’t worry about (it, him etc); doesn’t matter

管他三七二十一.pinyin: guǎn tā sān qī èr shí yī
管他三七二十一.definition: who cares; no matter what; regardless of the consequences

管他呢.definition: don’t worry about (it, him etc); doesn’t matter; whatever; anyway

管他的.definition: don’t worry about (it, him etc); doesn’t matter; whatever; anyway

管仲.definition: Guan Zhong (-645 BC), famous politician of Qi 齊國|齐国 of Spring and Autumn period; known as Guangzi 管子

管住.definition: to take control of; to manage; to curb

管住嘴邁開腿.pinyin: guǎn zhù zuǐ mài kāi tuǐ
管住嘴邁開腿.definition: lit. shut your mouth, move your legs (motto for losing weight)

管制.definition: to control; to restrict; (PRC law) non-custodial sentence with specified restrictions on one's activities for up to 3 years (e.g. not to participate in demonstrations)

管圓線蟲.definition: "eel worm", a parasitic worm carrying meningitis

管城區.definition: Guangcheng Hui District of Zhengzhou City 鄭州市|郑州市[Zheng4 zhou1 Shi4], Henan

管城回族區.definition: Guangcheng Hui District of Zhengzhou City 鄭州市|郑州市[Zheng4 zhou1 Shi4], Henan

管委會.definition: administrative committee; management committee; abbr. for 管理委員會|管理委员会[guan3 li3 wei3 yuan2 hui4]

管它.definition: no matter if; regardless of; don’t worry about (it, him etc); doesn’t matter

管家.definition: (old) butler; steward; manager; administrator; housekeeper; to manage a household

管家婆.definition: housewife (jocular); female housekeeper of a higher rank (old); busybody

管座.definition: to mount an electronic valve; to plug in a bulb

管待.definition: to wait on; to attend; to serve

管得著.definition: to concern oneself with (a matter); to make (sth) one's business

管手管腳.definition: to control in every detail; excessive supervision

管教.definition: to discipline; to teach; to guarantee

管教無方.definition: unable to discipline a child; incapable of dealing with (unruly child)

管束.definition: to exercise control over; restriction; control

管理.definition: to supervise; to manage; to administer; management; administration; CL:個|个[ge4]

管窺.definition: to look at sth through a bamboo tube; to have a restricted view

管線.definition: pipeline; general term for pipes, cables etc

管見.definition: my limited view (lit. view through a thin tube); my limited understanding; my opinion (humble)

管閒事.definition: to meddle; to be a "nosy Parker"; to be too inquisitive about other people's business
